  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "System Analyst",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>You will be part of PB platform delivery to ensure concise, coherent, consistent and quality delivery of the target business requirement.</p>\n<p>· Responsible for the overall system analysis activities; ensures high quality deliverables and meeting project schedules.</p>\n<p>· Address and resolve functional as well technical issues relating to the platform</p>\n<p>· Ensure functional knowledge is propagated downward to the project technical and QA teams so that quality testing is conducted and followed through</p>\n<p>· Support during testing phase of delivery to ensure the functional requirement is delivered as per FSD</p>\n<p>· Engage with system vendors to ensure business requirements/functionalities are clear for delivery of FSD throughout the end-to-end project implementation phases</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>· Experience in <strong>Temenos Wealthsuite</strong> product implementation is a must e.g. Version R23 or R24</p>\n<p>· Minimum <strong>3 years</strong> of hands-on working experience in <strong>TAP Core</strong> is a must</p>\n<p>· Experience in delivery of Private Banking solution and hands-on experience on at least <strong>2 end-to-end application delivery</strong></p>\n<p>· Implementation of Temenos TAP solution in a distributed bank’s ecosystem is desired</p>\n<p>· Experience in TAP version upgrade is desired</p>\n<p>· Experience in one of the TAP components like Wealth suite channels or WUI, WTX/ITX, Actuate, Odata is desired</p>\n<p>· Experience in Unix/Linux shell scripting</p>\n<p>· Experience in application solutioning as well as code review</p>\n<p>· Experience in end-to-end application delivery management in ensuring quality delivery</p>\n<p>· Experience in application delivery in ensuring full compliance of Bank’s policy and standard</p>\n<p>Experience in working with DevOps and Continuous integration with good understanding of n-Tier application architecture concepts</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Domain/ Technical Skills</strong></p>\n<p>· Private Banking, portfolio management</p>\n<p>Temenos Triple A Plus</p>",
